attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling their Nintendo Switch. They put the controllers into the handheld grip, then change them into the pad. They put the red joy-con controller and the joy-con strap together, and do the same with the other controller. They exchange a game card and an SD card. They turn on the pad, and then turn it off again.
